headline: Leidos to deliver seamless, secure data sharing across Department of Defense mission networks
summary: By modernizing the Defense Information Systems Agency (DISA) tools that transfer critical data between classified and unclassified networks, Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) will help accelerate decision making across the Department of Defense (DoD).
